From the co-creator of VeggieTales, Mike Nawrocki, comes a brand new series: The Dead Sea Squirrels.  Follow the hilarious and heartwarming adventures of 10-year-old Michael and his best friend Justin after they discover two petrified squirrels, Merle and Pearl, while on vacation near the Dead Sea. To their shock, the squirrels reawaken after 2,000 years!

Now living in modern-day America, Merle and Pearl adjust to the strange new world while sharing timeless wisdom rooted in biblical stories and values. Michael and Justin’s everyday lives become wild adventures filled with comical mishaps, heartfelt lessons, and faith-based life applications.

Through humor, action, and meaningful messages, Dead Sea Squirrels teaches kids about friendship, forgiveness, and doing what’s right—even when it’s hard. With its blend of biblical history and laugh-out-loud fun, the series delivers faith-filled entertainment for the whole family.
